OL,15,FCullimore, Julian Haviland, Richard
OL,16,FWakely (political), Richard Dixon
OL,17,F(industrial/economics), Tom St John
OL,18,FBarry (crime) and Gerald Seymour, Alan
OL,19,FHart, John Edwards, Sandy Gall, Richard
OL,20,FLindley (general reporters)."
